On Dec 15, 2004, at 12:27 PM, Stephen Diercouff wrote:

> Can the Bentley CDROM be made to work with VirtualPC on a Mac or not?

It should. Otherwise the program should be called Almost VirtualPC. 
There are reports, however, that it's difficult to install on 
ActualPCs, so you won't know whether any difficulty is with the 
emulator or with the application on the CD.
